evidence.text: All disputes in the docket relate to Temporary Restraining Orders (TROs) and amendments to court orders (e.g., 'MOTION for Temporary Restraining Order', 'ORDER granting 13 Motion for TRO', 'MOTION to Amend/Correct 23 Order on Motion for TRO'). The case involves court-ordered TROs, not negotiated settlements. The checklist explicitly excludes disputes over decrees (including TROs), and no settlement agreements or enforcement disputes were identified in any document.
